<plot>The undead on live TV? George Hamilton hosts a special on vampire legends, mixing taped segments with a live telecast from Transylvania (now Romania). Included: people claiming to be vampires; vampire expert and author Radu Florescu; and Bernard Davies of the Dracula Society, located in London.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?158766</url></doc>
